{"tid":2234371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大明年底前禁用膠飲管、膠袋等 目標2030年「走塑」","createTime":"2020-10-08T00:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T01:35:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be334c680aa4239469bb4146f6c5f7e267bd3184","tid":2234371,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"加拿大政府宣佈，在明年底全面禁止使用塑膠飲管、塑膠袋、塑膠飯盒等6種難以回收的即棄用品。當局強調，將與省級政府討論<span class=\"red\">如何</span><span class=\"red\">有效循環使用部分醫療裝備</span>，確保措施不會影響民眾及醫護人員使用個人保護裝備（PPE），應付武漢肺炎疫情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201008/5IFF2QKSDZBWTKNFO22MLWN3K4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2F5IFF2QKSDZBWTKNFO22MLWN3K4%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5JmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7dfc7587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2F5IFF2QKSDZBWTKNFO22MLWN3K4%2F&h=9704055c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201008/5IFF2QKSDZBWTKNFO22MLWN3K4/</a>"},{"pid":"7bd0ce46e36a3701705dd7a4b242cd80ad836c88","tid":2234371,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"環保撚喺時候出黎自慰"}]}